message: hello this board only turns on with the battery, when it has the battery and charger at the same time when pressing the power button it does not turn on

What is PPBUS_G3H voltage with only charger connected?
Also check 3V42_G3H.

only charger
PPBUS_G3H=8.58
3V42_G3H=3.42V
POWER BUTTON IS GOOD

Original 45/60W Magsafe 2 charger?

Check PM_BATLOW_L, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN, SMC_ADAPTER_EN, SMC_PM_G2_EN (charger alone).
3V3_S5/SUS come on?
Yes original charger 60w,     PM_BATLOW_L=3.3v PM_DSW_PWRGD=3.4v PCH_DSWVRMEN=3.2v SMC_ADAPTER_EN=3.3v SMC_PM_G2_EN3.4v 3V3_S5=3.3V  3V3_SUS=3.3V

Test if turns on in SMC bypass mode, with charger alone; also charger and battery.

Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L (in normal mode).
